Features:
1. The hands-free head massager enables you to enjoy great scalp massaging and head scratching experience, bringing you comfortable relaxation, it can effectively relieve stress, enhance blood circulation and improve insomnia.

2. Suitable for office workers, drivers, athletes, the elderly, fatigued people, laborers, and others suffering from headache or stress.

3. 4 optional vibration modes - active mode, relax mode, beauty mode, sleep mode. Each mode is different in massage manipulations and intensity, you can choose your favourite according to your own situations.

2. Suitable for office workers, drivers, athletes, the elderly, fatigued people, laborers, and others suffering from headache or stress.

4. One-key control, easy to start, it is friendly to starters and the elderly. Long press the power button for 3 sec to start or shut down the machine. To switch mode, press the same button again.
